comments: James (LAL) sets the screen in White's (CHI) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Williams (CHI) and James (LAC) briefly engage and separate during the screen.
LaVine (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position while defending James's (LAL) driving shot attempt.
Matthews (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position on LaVine (CHI) at the start of the drive.
Harrell (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by LaVine (CHI).
Schroder (LAL) sets the screen on Williams (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact as Williams moves under the screen.
Williams (CHI) makes contact with James's (LAL) arm and affects his driving shot attempt.
Young (CHI) sets the screen in Schroder's (LAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Schroder (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position on White (CHI) during the drive.
Temple (CHI) and James (LAL) make incidental contact as the players come together moving to the same spot.
Matthews (LAL) sets the screen on Williams (CHI) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Williams (CHI) makes incidental "high-five" contact with James (LAL) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Schroder (LAL) and Temple (CHI) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Young (CHI) sets the screen in Matthews's (LAL) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Harrell (LAL) makes incidental "high-five" contact with LaVine (CHI) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Temple (CHI) commits a take foul on Schroder (LAL).
